value: Breeds north and south of the Subtropical Convergence: Tristan da Cunha Group (Inaccessible, Tristan da Cunha, Nightingale, Gough), Prince Edward, Marion, Crozet (Hog, Possession, East), Kerguelen (uncommon), Amsterdam, and St. Paul Islands. Migratory: range at sea circumpolar in the austral seas between lat. 30° S. and the edge of the pack ice.
